{
  "texts": [
    "The following section will further explore the workings of LLMs, and their potential applications in mental health, and critically evaluate the opportunities and challenges they introduce.",
    "Large Language ModelsLLMs represent advancements in machine learning (ML), characterized by their ability to understand and generate human-like text with high accuracy [24].",
    "The efficacy of these models is typically evaluated using benchmarks designed to assess their linguistic fidelity and contextual relevance.",
    "Common metrics include BLEU for translation accuracy and ROUGE for summarization tasks [25].",
    "LLMs are characterized by their scale, often encompassing billions of parameters, setting them apart from traditional language models [26]."
  ]
}